"IO monad chain test: io.bind sequences two IO actions. Uses --allow-io."

` :suppress
echo-cmd: if(eu.os = "windows", "Write-Output hello", "echo hello")

` { target: :test requires-io: true }
test: io.bind(io.shell(echo-cmd), check-result)

check-result(r):
  io.return(if(r.stdout str.matches?("hello.*"),
    { RESULT: :PASS },
    { RESULT: :FAIL }))
